age-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%20have%20spiked%20to%207%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20their%20record%20lows%20of%20less%20than%203%25%20in%202021%2C%20which%20has%20not%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-mistake-buyers-sellers-mortgage-rates-time-to-buy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeterred%20prospective%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20changed%20the%20calculus%20for%20many%20sellers.%20Since%20most%20people%20have%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20buy%20another%20property%20to%20live%20in%2C%20even%20the%20ones%20who%20profit%20handsomely%20off%20a%20sale%20are%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20upgrade%20their%20digs%2C%20given%20the%20increased%20borrowing%20costs.%20It's%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20cruel%20summer%20for%20sellers%20who%20aren't%20ready%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20this%20new%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20could%20always%20be%20worse.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-bubble-home-prices-stay-high-crash-real-estate-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20signs%20that%20home%20prices%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20collapse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20more%20sales%20are%20happening%20now%20than%20a%20year%20ago.%20After%20all%2C%20people%20have%20to%20move%20for%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20life%20reasons%3B%20mortgage%20rates%20be%20damned.%20The%20number%20of%20homes%20for%20sale%20at%20any%20given%20moment%20is%20also%20growing%2C%20which%20means%20we're%20inching%20closer%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20market.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-ice-age-higher-home-prices-fewer-sales-inventory-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHousing%20Ice%20Age%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20slowly%20thawing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20peak%20months%20of%20home%20selling%2C%20which%20last%20from%20the%20spring%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20summer%2C%20may%20come%20with%20a%20rude%20awakening%20this%20year.%20Those%20who%20hoped%20that%20lower%20mortgage%20rates%20would%20grease%20the%20wheels%20of%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20nudging%20more%20buyers%20to%20get%20off%20the%20sidelines%20and%20bid%20up%20home%20prices%2C%20are%20realizing%20that%20dream%20scenario%20won't%20come%20to%20pass.%20Sellers%20may%20still%20have%20an%20advantage%2C%20but%20it's%20getting%20slimmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20hopeful%20sellers%20call%20up%20Eric%20Peterson%2C%20a%20real-estate%20broker%20in%20Austin%2C%20he%20usually%20asks%20them%20how%20much%20they%20think%20their%20home%20could%20fetch%20on%20the%20market.%20In%202021%20or%202022%2C%20before%20rising%20mortgage%20rates%20squashed%20buyer%20demand%2C%20people%20typically%20thought%20their%20homes%20were%20worth%20a%20lot%20less%20than%20what%20they%20could%20sell%20for%2C%20Peterson%20told%20me.%20Now%20when%20he%20poses%20the%20same%20question%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20usually%20overshooting%20it%20by%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20whiplash%20can%20leave%20today's%20sellers%20crestfallen%20in%20comparison.%20Austin%20was%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sell-house-right-now-austin-texas-market-selling-tips-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecities%20hit%20hardest%20by%20the%20pandemic%20hangover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20local%20home%20prices%20in%20March%20down%20roughly%2012%25%20from%20the%20peak%20in%20May%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Freddie%20Mac%20House%20Price%20Index.%20But%20while%20the%20city%20may%20be%20on%20the%20extreme%20end%20of%20things%2C%20sellers%20around%20the%20country%20face%20similar%20circumstances%3A%20There%20are%20fewer%20buyers%20out%20there%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20on%20the%20hunt%20have%20more%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20further%20and%20further%20we%20get%20from%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Peterson%20to