20these%20sellers%20will%20face%20a%20less%20favorable%20real-estate%20landscape.%20As%20more%20listings%20hit%20the%20market%20in%20the%20spring%20and%20summer%2C%20the%20number%20of%20homes%20for%20sale%20at%20any%20given%20moment%2C%20otherwise%20known%20as%20active%20inventory%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20grow.%20Nationwide%20inventory%20is%20up%2033%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faltosresearch.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousing-data%20firm%20Altos%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20homebuyers%20better%20odds%20of%20bargaining%20down%20prices%20and%20scoring%20concessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FwZ8iT%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Active%20inventory%20of%20single-family%20homes%20on%20the%20market%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20sale%20prices%20in%20March%20were%20up%20about%206.6%25%20from%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20but%20the%20leading%20indicators%20for%20deals%20that%20will%20close%20this%20summer%20%26quot%3Baren't%20nearly%20that%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Simonsen%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Altos%20Research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20weekly%20update.%20Prices%20on%20new%20listings%20across%20the%20country%20are%20basically%20flat%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20and%2033.5%25%20of%20single-family%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20have%20seen%20a%20cut%20from%20their%20original%20asking%20prices%2C%20the%20most%20of%20any%20April%20in%20a%20decade.%20Moody's%20Ratings%20now%20expects%20home%20values%20to%20rise%20a%20measly%201%25%20this%20year%20after%20a%206.5%25%20increase%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FebW74%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Median%20price%20of%20single-family%20homes%20on%20the%20market%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22393%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20once%20a%20price%20is%20agreed%20upon%2C%20sellers%20may%20have%20to%20shoulder%20more%20of%20the%20costs%20to%20complete%20the%20transaction%20than%20before.%20Unlike%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20a%20buyer%20might%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20%3Cem%3Eseller%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20pay%20for%20closing%20costs%20or%20pricey%20repairs%20that%20come%20up%20during%20an%20inspection.%20More%20than%20one-third%20of%20sellers%20gave%20concessions%20to%20buyers%20in%20the%20three%20months%20ending%20October%2031%2C%20Redfin%20found%2C%20up%20from%2027.6%25%20two%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjVYb6%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20single-family%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20with%20recent%20price%20reductions%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESellers%20across%20the%20country%20won't%20feel%20the%20pain%20equally%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20many%20will%20do%20just%20fine%20for%20themselves.%20In%20the%20Northeast%20and%20the%20West%2C%20active%20inventory%20is%20still%20more%20than%2030%25%20below%202019%20levels%2C%20keeping%20competition%20for%20homes%20tight.%20The%20situation%20will%20be%20toughest%20in%20places%20like%20Austin%20or%20Boise%2C%20Idaho%2C%20where%20wealthy%20out-of-towners%20drove%20up%20prices%20amid%20the%20pandemic.%20Now%20that%20people%20aren't%20moving%20across%20the%20country%20as%20much%2C%20it's%20harder%20to%20find%20the%20kinds%20of%20buyers%20willing%20to%20make%20outrageous%20bids%20for%20their%20slice%20of%20the%20Sun%20Belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FANwJL%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Median%20price%20of%20single-family%20homes%20under%20contract%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22429%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20listing%20homes%20for%20sale%20and%20they%20were%20selling%20for%20so%20much%20over%20asking%20price%2C%20there%20often%20wasn't%20a%20second%20buyer%20that%20was%20offering%20close%20to%20that%20final%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Peterson%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20market%20was%20very%20emotional%20in%20one%20direction.%20And%20I%20was%20warning%20everybody%3A%20All%20it%20takes%20is%20that%20one%20buyer%20to%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELibby%20Levinson-Katz%2C%20a%20broker%20in%20Denver%20and%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20local%20Realtor%20association's%20market-trends%20committee%2C%20said%20she's%20advising%20sellers%20there%20to%20price%20their%20homes%20conservatively%20and%20take%20care%20of%20big-ticket%20items%2C%20such%20as%20large%20repairs%2C%20before%20listing.%20Price-conscious%20buyers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-home-prices-mortgage-interest-affordability-crisis-janet-yellen-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20battling%20high%20rates%20and%20home%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20take%20on%20more%20expenses%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20get%20the%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20sellers%20need%20to%20kind%20of%20buckle%20the%20seatbelt%20and%20know%20that%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20going%20to%20be%20a%20quick%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20Levinson-Katz%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20take%20awhile%20because%20buyers%20are%20being%20really%20discerning%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELost%20in%20all%20this%20talk%20of%20sellers'%20woes%20is%20the%20simple%20fact%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomes-real-estate-how-to-fix-housing-crisis-factors-construction-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20home%20inventory%20is%20good%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sellers%20simply%20had%20too%20much%20power%20during%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20the%20pendulum%20swinging%20in%20the%20other%20direction%20just%20means%20we're%20slowly%20making%20our%20way%20toward%20a%20more%20balanced%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20many%20sellers%20end%20up%20also%20being%20buyers%20themselves%3A%20A%20whopping%2078%25%20of%20homeowners%20say%20they%20plan%20to%20buy%20again%20right%20after%20they%20sell%2C%20John%20Burns%20Research%20and%20Consulting%20found.%20So%20while%20it%20might%20be%20nice%20for%20sellers%20to%20watch%20their%20home%20values%20climb%20with%20each%20desperate%20bid%2C%20they'll%20probably%20have%20to%20join%20the%20masses%20clamoring%20over%20listings%20or%20worrying%20about%20the%20new%20reality%20of%20mortgage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealth-inequality-housing-market-interest-rates-wage-growth-inflation-mortgage-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmericans%20see%20their%20homes%20as%20not%20only%20shelter%20but%20also%20investment%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20weak%20sellers'%20market%20can%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20if%20prices%20plummet%2C%20buyers%20might%20not%20want%20to%20purchase%20homes%20for%20fear%20of%20catching%20a%20falling%20knife.%20This%20is%20why%20economists%20talk%20so%20much%20about%20the%20need%20for%20a%20balanced%20market%2C%20rather%20than%20one%20that%20simply%20favors%20affordability%20for%20buyers.%20It's%20a%20fine%20line%20to%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20slowdown%20for%20sellers%20may%20be%20good%20for%20the%20country's%20housing%20market%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20sudden%20switch-up%20can%20leave%20homeowners%20feeling%20like%20they%20missed%20the%20boat.%20About%2079%25%20of%20recent%20sellers%20in%20a%20survey%20from%20Realtor.com%20said%20they%20wished%20they%20had%20listed%20their%20home%20sooner%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20hotter%20market.%20But%20Peterson%20told%20me%20he%20tries%20to%20keep%20things%20in%20perspective%20for%20his%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20home%20prices%20are%20still%20up%20almost%2050%25%20from%20early%202020%20nationwide%2C%20according%20to%20Moody's%2C%20and%20about%2042%25%20in%20Austin.%20He%20warns%20sellers%20against%20comparing%20themselves%20with%20those%20who%20sold%20at%20the%20market's%20peak%2C%20when%20cheap%20money%20drove%20up%20prices.%20Back%20then%2C%20it%20didn't%20matter%20if%20you%20mispriced%20your%20home%20or%20neglected%20repairs%20%E2%80%94%20low%20interest%20rates%20and%20booming%20buyer%20interest%20practically%20ensured%20you'd%20find%20a%20more-than-willing%20taker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20always%20be%20tricky%20telling%20somebody%20that%20they%20were%20just%20lucky%20because%20it%20makes%20you%20sound%20envious%2C%26quot%3B%20Peterson%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%202.5%25%20interest%20rates%20can%20hide%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-sellers-summer-disappointment-mortgage-rates-house-prices-real-estate-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22pu