%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHilbert%20and%20her%20partner%20are%20big%20fans%20of%20Costco's%20%26quot%3BThat's%20It%26quot%3B%20fruit%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20they%20contain%20only%20dried%20fruit%20with%20no%20added%20sugar%20or%20other%20ingredients.%20They%20come%20in%20three%20flavors%3A%20strawberry%20and%20apple%2C%20mango%20and%20apple%2C%20or%20blueberry%20and%20apple.%20You%20can%20get%20a%20pack%20of%2024%20for%20%2415.99%20on%20the%20Costco%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20really%20great%2C%20especially%20if%20I%20need%20a%20quick%20snack%20before%20a%20workout%20or%20even%20after%20a%20workout%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHealthy%20carbohydrates%20such%20as%20fruits%20can%20help%20you%20perform%20better%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20the%20bars%20go%20well%20with%20a%20protein%20source%20like%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4c3bec2-8b8c-4742-b4c0-a89bb536971f%5C%22%3ENuts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20seeds%2C%20nuts%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20healthy%20fats%20and%20plant-based%20protein.%20They're%20a%20convenient%20and%20healthy%20snack%2C%20Hilbert%20said.%20She%20keeps%20packets%20of%20her%20favorite%20nuts%20in%20her%20desk%20drawer.%20The%20Kirkland%20Signature%20Organic%20range%20of%20nuts%2C%20which%20are%20Hilbert's%20favorite%2C%20have%20no%20added%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%20study%20found%20that%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffoods-live-10-years-longer-longevity-diet-study-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20eating%20lots%20of%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20whole%20grains%20and%20fruit%20in%20middle%20age%20could%20add%20years%20to%20a%20person's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHilbert's%20favorites%20are%20almonds%2C%20pistachios%2C%20cashews%2C%20and%20walnuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-health-dietitian-favorite-minimally-processed-fiber-costco-snacks-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715161259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310435ec0c696569ff1432%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-health-dietitian-favorite-minimally-processed-fiber-costco-snacks-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dietitian%20Megan%20Hilbert%20goes%20for%20snacks%20that%20are%20plant-based%2C%20minimally%20processed%2C%20and%20high%20in%20fiber%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20gut%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-health-dietitian-favorite-minimally-processed-fiber-costco-snacks-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20Retort%20To%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20Racist%20Flub%2C%20BJP%20Leaders'%20'Look%20Indian'%20Posts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETearing%20into%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20veteran%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-news-people-in-east-look-chinese-south-like-africa-sam-pitroda-triggers-row-5615438%5C%22%3Efresh%20flub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20demanded%20a%20response%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20tolerate%20disrespect%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20colour%20of%20skin%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20whose%20remark%20on%20an%20inheritance%20tax%20in%20the%20US%20last%20month%20left%20the%20Congress%20red-faced%20in%20the%20election%20season%2C%20came%20up%20with%20a%20new%20howler%20while%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20pitch%20for%20national%20unity%20despite%20India's%20diversity.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20The%20Statesman%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20described%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B...%20diverse%20country...%20where%20people%20on%20East%20look%20like%20Chinese%2C%20people%20on%20West%20look%20like%20Arab%2C%20people%20on%20North%20look%20like%20maybe%20White%20and%20people%20in%20South%20look%20like%20Africa%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushed%20into%20firefight%20mode%2C%20the%20Congress%20distanced%20itself%20from%20its%20senior%20leader's%20remark.%20%26quot%3BThe%20analogies%20drawn%20by%20Mr.%20Sam%20Pitroda%20in%20a%20podcast%20to%20illustrate%20India's%20diversity%20are%20most%20unfortunate%20and%20unacceptable.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20completely%20dissociates%20itself%20from%20these%20analogies%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20analogies%20drawn%20by%20Mr.%20Sam%20Pitroda%20in%20a%20podcast%20to%20illustrate%20India's%20diversity%20are%20most%20unfortunate%20and%20unacceptable.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20completely%20dissociates%20itself%20from%20these%20analogies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1788106840091291988%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20videos%20of%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Telangana's%20Warangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20his%20%26quot%3Bshehzade%20(prince)%26quot%3B%20barb%20for%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShehzade%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20answer.%20The%20country%20will%20not%20tolerate%20the%20disrespect%20of%20our%20countrymen%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20colour%20of%20skin.%20Modi%20will%20definitely%20not%20tolerate%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20now%20knows%20why%20the%20Congress%20opposed%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20for%20the%20President's%20post.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20wonder%20why%20the%20Congress%20opposed%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20candidature%20in%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20but%20I%20could%20not%20understand.%20But%20now%20I%20know%20why%20they%20tried%20to%20defeat%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20an%20adivasi.%20An%20uncle%20of%20the%20shehzaada%20stays%20in%20the%20US.%20He%20is%20his%20philosopher%20and%20guide.%20He%20has%20said%20those%20who%20have%20dark%20skin%20are%20from%20Africa.%20Now%20I%20have%20understood%2C%20they%20also%20thought%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20is%20African.%20They%20thought%20her%20skin%20is%20dark%2C%20so%20she%20must%20be%20defeated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20X%20handle%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20disgusted%20by%20the%20remarks%20of%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20is%20the%20friend%2C%20philosopher%20and%20guide%20of%20the%20Congress'%20Crown%20Prince%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHis%20remarks%20are%20racist%20and%20in%20very%20poor%20taste%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20tweeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20came%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20remarks%20of%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Congress's%20overseas%20wing.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20told%20the%20media%20that%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20statements%20%26quot%3Bshow%20his%20ignorance%20and%20contempt%20for%20the%20fundamental%20identity%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda's%20racist%20remarks%20came%20when%20he%20was%20speaking%20about%20the%20country's%20diversity.%20He%C2%A0referred%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20divided%20country%20today%20based%20on%20ideas%20of%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20who%20is%20right%20or%20wrong...%20but%20a%20question%20of%20what%20you%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20there%20is%20another%20view%20that%20says%20our%20founding%20fathers%20fought%20the%20British%20Raj%20not%20for%20a%20Hindu%20nation%20but%20for%20a%20secular%20nation.%20Pakistan%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20nation%20based%20on%20religion...%20you%20can%20see%20how%20that%20is%20going.%20We%20are%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20world.%20We%20have%20survived%2070-75%20years%20in%20a%20very%20happy%20environment%2C%20leaving%20aside%20a%20few%20fights%20here%20and%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20are%20all%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20we%20respect%20different%20languages%2C%20religions%2C%20customs%2C%20and%20food.%20As%20a%20Gujarati%2C%20I%20love%20dosa.%20So%2C%20if%20I%20go%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20speak%20the%20local%20language%2C%20it%20is%20ok.%20I%20am%20still%20at%20home...%20that%20is%20my%20India%2C%20rooted%20in%20democracy%2C%20freedom%2C%20liberty%2C%20and%20fraternity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%20This%20view%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20being%20challenged%20by%20one%20that%20includes%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20Ram%20Navami%20and%20the%20PM%20going%20to%20temples%20all%20the%20time%20and%20talking%20not%20as%20a%20national%20leader%2C%20but%20that%20of%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20panned%20the%20remarks%20were%20its%20Northeast%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Assam's%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20and%20Manipur's%20N%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESam%20bhai%2C%20I%20am%20from%20the%20North%20East%20and%20I%20look%20like%20an%20Indian.%20We%20are%20a%20diverse%20country%20-%20we%20may%20look%20different%20but%20we%20are%20all%20one.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHamare%20desh%20ke%20bare%20mein%20thoda%20