%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20it%20works%20is%20you%20subscribe%20to%20the%20website%2C%20make%20a%20profile%2C%20and%20list%20your%20home.%20You%20describe%20yourself%20and%20your%20traveling%20members%20and%20talk%20about%20your%20home%20and%20what%20you%20have%20to%20offer%2C%20as%20well%20as%20where%20you%20want%20to%20travel.%20Then%2C%20you%20start%20looking%20for%20people%20in%20that%20area%20who%20are%20on%20HomeExchange%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20different%20kinds%20of%20exchanges.%20It's%20quite%20flexible.%20There's%20a%20simultaneous%20reciprocal%20exchange%20where%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-swap-homes-on-facebook-tiktok-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswap%20houses%20with%20another%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20so%20they%20come%20to%20stay%20in%20your%20house%2C%20and%20you%20stay%20in%20theirs.%20That%20works%20well%20for%20families%20and%20people%20who%20have%20one%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20reciprocal%20exchange%20where%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20swap%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20so%20that's%20good%20for%20people%20who%20have%20second%20homes.%20The%20most%20flexible%20way%20is%20to%20use%20guest%20points.%20When%20somebody%20comes%20to%20stay%20in%20your%20house%2C%20the%20website%20gives%20you%20an%20allotted%20amount%20of%20guest%20points%2C%20which%20vary%20according%20to%20how%20large%20your%20home%20is%2C%20how%20many%20people%20you%20can%20accommodate%2C%20and%20what%20facilities%20you%20have.%20You%20can%20then%20use%20those%20points%20whenever%20you%20want.%20That's%20what%20we%20use%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Italy%20up%20until%20last%20year%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20much%20larger%20home%20with%20a%20separate%20self-contained%20apartment.%20We%20would%20mostly%20swap%20with%20people%20from%20Australia%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-best-ways-to-save-money-travel-tips-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20liked%20to%20come%20to%20Italy%20during%20our%20summer%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20go%20in%20their%20summer%2C%20which%20are%20different%20times%20of%20the%20year.%20So%2C%20we%20would%20be%20at%20home%20when%20they%20came%2C%20and%20they%20would%20stay%20in%20our%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20UK%20last%20year.%20We%20had%20our%20first%20guest%20in%20this%20house%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago.%20We%20did%20a%20hospitality%20exchange%2C%20which%20is%20where%20you%20stay%20at%20home%20and%20host%20people.%20I%20like%20to%20cook%20and%20entertain%20for%20them.%20We've%20got%20some%20Australians%20coming%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julie%20Williams%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Australia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ac026b4abc992e8c6c253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Williams%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Australia.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julie%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22014278e9-f470-45c7-93d8-f9c507ade3a7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20meet%20all%20sorts%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20complete%20cross-section%20of%20people%20and%20all%20ages.%20We've%20met%20doctors%2C%20people%20who%20work%20for%20NASA%2C%20academics%2C%20people%20who%20aren't%20necessarily%20professionals%2C%20and%20even%20people%20with%20plenty%20of%20money.%20We%20even%20hosted%20a%20senator%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktokers-share-home-tours-house-swaps-the-holiday-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20fed%20up%20being%20in%20hotels%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%20if%20they%20travel%20a%20lot.%20They%20want%20to%20live%20like%20locals%20when%20they%20go%20on%20holiday.%20They%20don't%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20hotel%20and%20just%20be%20a%20tourist.%20We%20always%20tell%20people%20all%20the%20local%20places%20to%20go%20and%20things%20to%20see%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20have%20known%20about%20if%20they%20weren't%20staying%20with%20us.%20That's%20a%20big%20driver%20for%20people%20who%20get%20the%20bug%20for%20HomeExchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20stayed%20in%20places%20in%20Australia%20that%20are%20totally%20off%20the%20grid%20in%20conservation%20areas%20that%20don't%20have%20electricity.%20That's%20completely%20different%20than%20being%20in%20a%20hotel%20and%20getting%20dressed%20up%20to%20go%20down%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20kept%20in%20contact%20with%20some%20people%20we've%20met%20and%20even%20become%20friends.%20Our%20first%20exchange%20was%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20on%20St.%20John%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fislands-americans-can-travel-to-without-passport-photos-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Virgin%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20stayed%20with%20some%20people%20there%20who%20later%20came%20to%20stay%20with%20us%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julie%20Williams%20in%20Raratonga%2C%20Cook%20Islands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ac087b4abc992e8c6c257%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulie%20Williams%20in%20Rarotonga%2C%20Cook%20Islands.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Julie%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c91ab22f-daa9-40ee-b3c7-8443444af8c3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20were%20hooked%20after%20our%20first%20exchange%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20pretty%20much%20hooked%20after%20our%20first%20trip.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20I%20was%20coming%20up%20on%2050%20and%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20Australia.%20I%20put%20together%20a%20massive%20three-month%20trip%2C%2012%20weeks%20of%20back-to-back%20home%20exchanges%20around%20Australia%20and%20Tasmania.%20We%20had%20a%20stopover%20in%20Singapore%20on%20the%20way%20back.%20We%20couldn't%20have%20afforded%20to%20do%20a%20trip%20like%20that%20if%20we%20were%20staying%20in%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeExchange%20means%20we%20can%20travel%20for%20much%20longer.%20The%20winters%20in%20Italy%20were%20cold%20and%20snowy%2C%20so%20we%20would%20often%20go%20away%20for%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20time%20using%20the%20website%2C%20I've%20been%20to%20Nevis%2C%20St.%20Martin%2C%20St.%20John%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Australia%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimbing-sea-stacks-in-tasmania-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETasmania%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Rarotonga%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Cook%20Island%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbali-indonesia-travel-tips-before-visiting-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20England%2C%20Ireland%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Italy%2C%20Denmark%2C%20Belgium%2C%20Holland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Western%20Australia%2C%20we%20once%20stayed%20outside%20a%20place%20called%20Monkey%20Mia%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Inglou%20Reef%20in%20somebody's%20beach%20house.%20We%20went%20to%20Monkey%20Mia%2C%20where%20wild%20dolphins%20come%20in%20to%20feed.%20They're%20completely%20wild.%20It%20was%20my%20dream%20to%20be%20picked%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20water%20and%20hold%20the%20fish%20to%20see%20if%20the%20dolphin%20wanted%20to%20come%20and%20eat%20it.%20And%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20to%20a%20fantastic%20place%20in%20Bali%20where%20we%20stayed%20in%20a%20beautiful%20villa%20with%20staff%2C%20a%20driver%2C%20and%20someone%20cooking%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20we've%20saved%