B%22title%22%3A%22I%20worked%20at%20SpaceX%20where%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20a%20cubicle%20away.%20At%20Elon's%20companies%2C%20it's%20add%20value%20or%20leave.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Employees%20at%20SpaceX%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a43e710dfcda4096777d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECHANDAN%20KHANNA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVincent%20Peters%20worked%20in%20military%20compliance%20when%20he%20was%20poached%20to%20work%20at%20SpaceX.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20the%20work%20culture%20was%20ruthlessly%20efficient%20and%20you%20could%20see%20Musk%20on%20the%20office%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20need%20your%20hand%20held%2C%20the%20former%20employee%20said%20to%20avoid%20Musk's%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Vincent%20Peters%2C%20founder%20of%20Inheritance%20AI%20and%20former%20SpaceX%20employee%20discussing%20his%20career%20path%20and%20experience%20at%20SpaceX.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20graduated%20from%20West%20Point%20in%202005%20at%2023.%20Shortly%20before%20graduating%2C%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20allergy-induced%20asthma.%20So%20I%20graduated%20on%20medical%20leave%2C%20couldn't%20be%20deployed%2C%20and%20continued%20on%20medical%20leave%20for%20another%20six%20months%20before%20being%20discharged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20internships%20or%20corporate%20experience%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20while%20to%20transition%20into%20the%20workforce.%20Once%20I%20did%2C%20I%20went%20on%20to%20work%20in%20many%20different%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223de7c6d-a933-408b-a720-5627a899fd0a%5C%22%3EThe%20beginning%20of%20my%20corporate%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20contractor%20job%20with%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20gained%20experience%20doing%20business%20administration%2C%20research%2C%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20got%20work%20more%20aligned%20with%20my%20degree%20in%20systems%20engineering%20and%20technology%20as%20a%20security%20project%20manager%20at%20Freddie%20Mac.%20I%20stayed%20in%20banking%20but%20moved%20into%20working%20on%20compliance%20and%20risk%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20left%20the%20banking%20industry%20to%20partner%20with%20one%20of%20my%20best%20friends%20from%20West%20Point%2C%20who%20owned%20a%20tech%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F2twelvesolutions.com%2FV2%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2%20Twelve%20Solutions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20worked%20in%20%26quot%3Bauthority%20to%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20certifying%20what%20technology%20can%20be%20used%20for%20US%20Government%20military%20missions.%20We%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pitch%20our%20services%20to%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20introduced%20to%20people%20on%20the%20SpaceX%20Mission%20team%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20interview%20with%20them%20for%20a%20job%20at%20SpaceX.%20After%20a%20long%20process%20with%20multiple%20conversations%2C%20they%20offered%20me%20a%20job%20doing%20information%20compliance%20and%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20said%20no%2C%20but%20after%20their%20counteroffer%2C%20I%20had%20to%20tell%20my%20friend%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%2C%20but%20I'm%20going%20to%20go%20work%20for%20SpaceX.%26quot%3B%20I%20started%20in%20November%202018.%20My%20primary%20role%20was%20showing%20government%20clients%20that%20SpaceX%20was%20compliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20project%20was%20the%20Commercial%20Crew%20program%20where%20astronauts%20needed%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20by%20US%20space%20capabilities.%20SpaceX%20was%20one%20of%20the%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2Fnasa-commercial-crew-the-astronauts-spacex-and-boeing-will-launch.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eawarded%20that%20contract%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20brought%20on%20to%20engage%20with%20NASA%20and%20show%20SpaceX%20was%20compliant.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20supported%20some%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20customers%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Artemis%20program%20to%20return%20to%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc9057ca-809d-40b7-8239-30790643d619%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20working%20at%20SpaceX%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20is%20the%20most%20efficient%20company%20I've%20ever%20worked%20for.%20Instead%20of%20having%20a%20manager%20and%20a%20list%20of%20tasks%2C%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20sit%20in%20on%20meetings%20and%20add%20value%20to%20projects%20aligned%20with%20my%20interests%20or%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20would%20get%20fired%20every%20day%20during%20the%20first%20six%20months.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20there%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20to%20do.%20In%20the%20military%2C%20there%20was%20a%20change%20of%20command.%20At%20SpaceX%2C%20you%20ask%20yourself%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20do%20this%20thing%3F%20How%20do%20we%20do%20it%20safely%3F%20How%20do%20we%20do%20it%20so%20that%20it's%20a%20good%20value%20for%20our%20customers%3F%26quot%3B%20Then%20you%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20boundaries%20in%20my%20role%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20adding%20value%20to%20whatever%20I%20was%20working%20on.%20For%20example%2C%20someone%20would%20ask%20if%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20flight%20software%2C%20and%20if%20I%20were%2C%20I'd%20be%20invited%20to%20attend%20those%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20directive%20was%20if%20I%20was%20in%20a%20meeting%20and%20it%20was%20adding%20value%20to%20what%20I%20did%20daily%2C%20stay%2C%20or%20if%20I%20was%20adding%20value%20based%20on%20my%20expertise%2C%20stay%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20neither%20of%20those%20things%20were%20happening%2C%20you%20should%20get%20up%20and%20respectfully%20walk%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%2C%20a%20government%20customer%20came%20in%20with%20a%2050-slide%20deck.%20Six%20slides%20into%20the%20presentation%2C%2075%25%20of%20the%20room%20had%20walked%20out.%20I%20had%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20if%20he%20didn't%20get%20to%20the%20point%2C%20I'd%20be%20the%20only%20person%20left%20in%20the%20room%20%E2%80%94%20and%20only%20because%20I%20had%20to%20walk%20him%20out.%20He%20skipped%20ahead%20to%20his%20last%20five%20slides.%20That%20kind%20of%20environment%20makes%20you%20much%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20everyone%20is%20accessible.%20You're%20all%20in%20cubicles%2C%20including%20Elon%20and%20the%20COO%2C%20Gwynne%20Shotwell.%20You%20can%20look%20up%2C%20be%20seen%2C%20and%20say%20to%20people%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I%20need%20this.%26quot%3B%20It's%20very%20open%20and%20makes%20collaborating%20and%20getting%20to%20know%20people%20easy.%20The%20only%20fixed%20offices%20are%20for%20people%20who%20often%20need%20to%20have%20confidential%20conversations%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20head%20of%20human%20resources%20and%20the%20CFO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247737056-5f88-462e-b4c6-ff928de26736%5C%22%3EWorking%20on%20Starlink%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quickly%20found%20that%20once%20you're%20in%20the%20circle%20of%20trust%20within%20Elon%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20you%20get%20a%20job%20more%20easily%20at%20another%20company%20in%20the%20portfolio.%20For%20example%2C%20someone%20who%20started%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20me%20at%20SpaceX%20is%20running%20IT%20at%20X%20now%20%E2%80%94%20the%20culture%20is%20just%20to%20do%20whatever%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mentality%20is%20how%20I%20started%20working%20on%20Starlink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Starlink%20team%20had%20several%20questions%20from%20the%20Canadian%20communications%20regulators.%20They%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20SpaceX%20was%20handling%20Starlink%20customer%20data%20and%20the%20configuration%20of%20some%20Starlink%20ground%20systems%20that%20were%20built%20and%20maintained%20by%20SpaceX.%20With%20my%20background%20in%20government%20work%20and%20compliance%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20natural%20fit%20for%20me%20to%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20I%20asked%20to%20help%20and%20was%20allowed%20to%20work%20on%20their%20projects%20in%20addition%20to%20my%20work%20at%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c9a2361-4e8c-4419-aa21-09b7e5c3e2d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20work%20is%20rigorous%2C%20but%20people%20are%20very%20accepting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20accepting%20work%20culture%20I've%20ever%20participated%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20also%20wasn't%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20placed%20on%20where%20people%20went%20to%20school.%20Some%20of%20the%20most%20intelligent%20people%20I%20worked%20with%20there%20were%20high%20school%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20your%20background%20or%20credentials%2C%20it's%20a%20place%20where%20you%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20yourself%20accountable.%20It's%20assumed%20that%20you%20should%20know%20what%20you%20should%20be%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20boss%20to%20hold%20your%20hand%20and%20tell%20you%20what%20you%20need%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20do%20it%2C%20you%20will%20be%20disappointed%20working%20with%20Elon.%20But%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20boss%20who%20trusts%20in%20your%20decision-making%2C%20you'll%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ultimately%20left%20in%20February%202022%20because%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20learning.%20While%20SpaceX%20was%20one%20of%20my%20best%20work%20experiences%2C%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20high%20turnover%20rate%20where%20people%20would%20leave%20between%20their%20first%20and%20second%20years.%20After%20my%20third%20year%2C%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20senior%20in%20my%20group%2C%20and%20there%20weren't%20many%20people%20to%20learn%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6382460-66de-4ef4-b253-1b21d53ef779%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20time%20at%20SpaceX%20has%20helped%20me%20run%20my%20own%20company%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20started%20my%20new%20project%2C%20Inheritance%20Art%2C%20in%20early%202022.%20We're%20working%20on%20various%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20from%20crypto%20to%20large%20language%20model%20services%20and%20even%20creating%20our%20own%20AI%20models.%20I'm%20enjoying%20the%20challenge%2C%20but%20I%20still%20look%20back%20fondly%20on%20my%20time%20at%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20SpaceX%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20hire%20and%20manage%20people%20efficiently%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20never%20a%20fan%20of%20middle%20management%2C%20and%20my%20experience%20there%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20run%20an%20organization%20without%20it.%20Space%20X%20is%20a%20flat%20organization%2C%20and%20it%20works%20well%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-work-at-spacex-elon-musk-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715160084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a459410dfcda40967798c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-work-at-spacex-elon-musk-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vincent%20Peters%20spent%20four%20years%20working%20at%20SpaceX%20in%20compliance.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20the%20most%20efficient%20company%20he'd%20ever%20worked%20at.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jamie%20Killin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-work-at-spacex-elon-musk-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7