Saturn%20V%20rocket%20that%20took%20Mr%20Armstrong%20and%20Mr%20Aldrin%20to%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bill%20Kaysing%20self-published%20a%20pamphlet%20that%20contained%20some%20outrageous%20theories.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Bill%20Kaysing%20self-published%20a%20pamphlet%20that%20contained%20some%20outrageous%20theories.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjt4ubmio_bill-kaysing_625x300_08_May_24.png%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBill%20Kaysing%20self-published%20a%20pamphlet%20that%20contained%20some%20outrageous%20theories.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20billkaysing.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvinced%20in%20his%20belief%2C%20Mr%20Kaysing%20self-published%20a%20pamphlet%20'We%20Never%20Went%20to%20the%20Moon%3A%20America's%20Thirty%20Billion%20Dollar%20Swindle'%20that%20contained%20grainy%20photos%20and%20some%20outrageous%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20questioned%20why%20there%20are%20no%20stars%20in%20the%20pictures%20of%20the%20Moon%20landing%20released%20by%20the%20US%20government.%20Further%2C%20Mr%20Kaysing%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20is%20no%20blast%20crater%20under%20the%20landing%20module%2C%20along%20with%20highlighting%20the%20way%20the%20shadows%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20well%20documented%20that%20NASA%20was%20often%20badly%20managed%20and%20had%20poor%20quality%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kaysing%20told%20%3Cem%3EWired%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201994.%20%26quot%3BBut%20as%20of%201969%2C%20we%20could%20suddenly%20perform%20manned%20flight%20upon%20manned%20flight%3F%20With%20complete%20success%3F%20It's%20just%20against%20all%20statistical%20odds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20his%20death%20in%202005%2C%20he%20maintained%20that%20the%20whole%20thing%20was%20a%20fraud%2C%20filmed%20in%20a%20TV%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20queries%20created%20doubt%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people%20that%20are%20kept%20alive%20even%20today%20in%20Hollywood%20movies%20and%20%3Cem%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20documentaries%2C%20Reddit%20forums%20and%20YouTube%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20believe%20and%20raise%20doubt%20on%20NASA's%20mission%20are%20podcaster%20Joe%20Rogan%20and%20YouTuber%20Shane%20Dawson.%20A%20sociology%20professor%20in%20New%20Jersey%20was%20exposed%20last%20year%20for%20telling%20his%20students%20the%20landings%20were%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20has%20expressed%20disappointment%20on%20the%20propagation%20of%20these%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%2C%20the%20internet%20has%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20people%20to%20say%20whatever%20the%20hell%20they%20like%20to%20a%20broader%20number%20of%20people%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Roger%20Launius%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20historian%20of%20NASA%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20Americans%20love%20conspiracy%20theories.%20Every%20time%20something%20big%20happens%2C%20somebody%20has%20a%20counter-explanation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20presented%20extraordinary%20volume%20of%20evidence%20-%20382%20kg%20of%20Moon%20rock%20collected%20across%20six%20missions%3B%20corroboration%20from%20Russia%2C%20Japan%20and%20China%3B%20and%20images%20from%20the%20Nasa%20Lunar%20Reconnaissance%20Orbiter%20showing%20the%20tracks%20made%20by%20the%20astronauts%20in%20the%20Moondust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Moon-hoax%20conspiracy%20has%20blossomed%20since%201969.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715159340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2jr8bmt_neil-armstrong-moon-landing_625x300_08_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fpeople-think-1969-moon-landing-was-faked-and-one-man-is-to-be-blamed-5616475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bill%20Kaysing%20loosely%20worked%20on%20t