n%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20this%20pervasive%20fragrance%20in%20our%20Garden%20of%20Time%3F%20Can%20we%20pick%20the%20notes%3F%20Is%20it%20that%20of%20dissent%20or%20conformity%3F%20Is%20the%20garden%20resonant%20with%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20west%20wind%20or%20does%20Nero's%20lyre%20pulse%20through%20its%20nooks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20many%20of%20us%20find%20questions%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20relevance%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmet-gala%5C%22%3EMet%20Gala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fashion's%20biggest%20evening%20out.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpro-palestine-protesters-rally-outside-met-gala-event-several-arrested-5605565%5C%22%3Edissing%20voices%20are%20particularly%20louder%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20given%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20arrests%20across%20university%20campuses%20not%20very%20far%20from%20the%20Metropolitan%20Museum%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20gala's%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theme%20of%20this%20year's%20Met%20Gala%20is%20'The%20Garden%20of%20Time'%2C%20and%20it%20could%20not%20have%20been%20more%20appropriate%20in%20at%20least%20a%20slightly%20perverse%20sense.%20With%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20torn%20apart%20by%20ongoing%20wars%20and%20violence%2C%20a%20rumination%20on%20time%20and%20its%20passage%20is%20essential%20to%20retain%20perspective.%20Is%20time%20really%20an%20objective%20concept%3F%20If%20so%2C%20why%20does%20it%20not%20pass%20with%20equal%20speed%20for%20the%20aggressor%20and%20the%20victim%3F%20Why%20does%20it%20stand%20still%20for%20the%20weaker%20side%3F%20(Actually%2C%20Henri%20Bergson%20told%20us%20the%20reasons%20long%20ago).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFashion%20As%20A%20Reminder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20sound%20discordant%20to%20raise%20these%20metaphysical%20questions%20amidst%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20physical%20and%20the%20material.%20And%20the%20latter%20should%20be%20celebrated.%20Fashion%20is%20both%20the%20celebration%20and%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20undeniable%20corporeality%20of%20human%20existence.%20We%20exist%20as%20bodies%20and%20therefore%20we%20are.%20Bodies%20precede%20ideas.%20The%20moment%20our%20bodies%20go%20away%2C%20our%20existence%20-%20however%20rarefied%20or%20fetishised%20in%20intellectual%20terms%20-%20fades.%20Nobody%20knows%20this%20better%20than%20those%20witnessing%20the%20destruction%20and%20desecration%20of%20bodies%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFashion%20brings%20back%20attention%20to%20the%20body.%20It%20also%2C%20often%2C%20ends%20up%20idealising%20the%20body.%20There%20is%20no%20end%20to%20the%20debate%20on%20what%20the%20function%20of%20fashion%20is%20or%20ought%20to%20be.%20This%20is%20not%20even%20the%20time%20to%20get%20into%20that%20debate%20anyway.%20As%20a%20socio-economic%20activity%2C%20fashion%20has%20its%20role%20cut%20out.%20As%20an%20assemblage%20of%20ideas%2C%20it%20often%20leaves%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired.%20Fashion%20exists%20between%20the%20two%20extremes%20of%20Karl%20Marx's%20war%20cry%20to%20politicise%20art%20and%20its%20later%20rejection%20by%20the%20proponents%20of%20Aestheticism.%20Those%20who%20were%20chanting%20'art%20for%20art's%20sake'%2C%20%3Cem%3El'art%20pour%20l'art%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%2C%20much%20later%2C%20%3Cem%3Ears%20gratia%20artist%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E-%20the%20motto%20of%20Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer%20Studios%2C%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ELessons%20From%20Faiz%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20fashion%20confuses%20us%20when%20we%20start%20'thinking'%20about%20it.%20But%20think%20we%20must.%20And%20not%20just%20about%20how%20various%20designers%20and%20connoisseurs%20interpreted%20the%20theme%20this%20year.%20Truth%20be%20told%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwebstories%2Ffeature%2Fmet-gala-2024-all-you-need-to-know-16266%5C%22%3Ethis%20year's%20Met%20Gala%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20go%20down%20in%20its%20history%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20lacklustre%20editions.%20How%20many%20iterations%20of%20the%20'naked%20dress'%20can%20one%20stomach%20in%20a%20single%20evening%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Flifestyle%2Fmet-gala-2024-from-hummingbird-earrings-to-berry-embellished-sleeves-zendayas-jewel-toned-john-galliano-met-gala-gown-was-straight-from-the-garden-of-5605210%5C%22%3EAnd%20Zendaya%3C%2Fa%3E%20does%20not%20even%20need%20a%20Met%20Gala%20to%20establish%20her%20supremacy%20in%20the%20world%20of%20fashion.%20So%2C%20what%20should%20we%20talk%20about%20when%20we%20think%20and%20talk%20about%20fashion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20prescriptive%20way%20of%20approaching%20the%20fashion%20discourse.%20Politics%20alone%20can%20not%20be%20it.%20Some%20thoughtless%20acts%20of%20blending%20politics%20and%20fashion%20are%20more%20disastrous%20than%20a%20badly%20blended%20foundation.%20Take%20the%20just%20concluded%20Mumbai%20Fashion%20Week%2C%20for%20example.%20Several%20designers%20tried%20to%20mask%20their%20lack%20of%20creative%20ingenuity%20behind%20socio-political%20grandstanding.%20This%20is%20a%20double%20fraud%20-%20against%20fashion%20and%20against%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaiz%20Ahmad%20Faiz%20gave%20certain%20lessons%20in%20dealing%20with%20ideas%20that%20are%20not%20natural%20bedfellows.%20His%20poem%20'%3Cem%3EMujhse%20pahli%20si%20mohabbat%20mere%20mahboob%20na%20maang...%3C%2Fem%3E'%20depicts%20the%20human%20state%20as%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Ean-ginat%20sadiyo%C3%B1%20ke%20t%C4%81r%C4%ABk%20bah%C4%ABm%C4%81na%20tilism%3Cbr%3E%5Cnresham%20o%20atlas%20o%20kam%E1%B8%B3h%C4%81b%20me%C3%B1%20bunv%C4%81.e%20hue%3Cbr%3E%5Cnj%C4%81-ba-j%C4%81%20bikte%20hue%20k%C5%ABcha-o-b%C4%81z%C4%81r%20me%C3%B1%20jism%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E1%B8%B3haak%20me%C3%B1%20luTh%E1%B8%8Ce%20hue%20%E1%B8%B3huun%20me%C3%B1%20nahl%C4%81.e%20hue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20being%20a%20cursed%20maze%2C%20or%20marketplace%2C%20crafted%20out%20of%20expensive%20and%20exquisite%20fabrics%20like%20silk%20and%20brocade%2C%20where%20bodies%20are%20bought%20and%20sold%20...%20The%20duality%20of%20excess%20and%20deprivation%20is%20enunciated%20radically%20in%20this%20poem.%20Faiz%20does%20not%20diss%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20fabric%20or%20the%20artistic%20vision%20that%20has%20painstakingly%20brought%20beautiful%20motifs%20on%20silk%20turning%20it%20into%20the%20prized%20'%3Cem%3Ekimkhaab%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20He%2C%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20is%20giving%20a%20hat%20tip%20to%20the%20sweat%20and%20blood%20of%20the%20working%20classes%20that%20create%20such%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20Fashion%20Seems%20Incompatible%20With%20Radical%20Change%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFashion%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20industries%20in%20the%20world%2C%202%25%20of%20the%20global%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20(GDP)%2C%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20cannot%20be%20ignored%20by%20even%20the%20unfashionable.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20protesters%20gathered%20outside%20the%20Met%20demanding%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20divestment.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20their%20demands%20will%20be%20heard%20any%20more%20here%20than%20on%20the%20university%20campuses%20or%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Congress.%20But%20that's%20alright.%20Both%20can%20and%20ought%20to%20coexist.%20That%20they%20appear%20incompatible%20is%20a%20function%20of%20a%20historical%20alliance%20of%20the%20fashionable%20with%20the%20cruel%20and%20the%20indifferent.%20That%20needs%20to%20change.%20Fashion's%20potential%20for%20radical%20change%20by%20demanding%20what%20is%20ethically%20sustainable%20is%20still%20untapped.%20When%20it%20is%20realised%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20moment%20to%20reckon%20with%2C%20and%20the%20placards%20might%20say%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Sleeping%20Beauties%3A%20Reawakening%20Fashion'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20theme%20of%20the%202024-25%20exhibition%20that%20the%20Met%20Gala%20celebrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam