20Congress%20leader%20had%20gone%20silent%20on%20his%20%26quot%3BAmbani-Adani%26quot%3B%20offensive%20since%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20five%20years%2C%20Congress's%20shehzade%20kept%20chanting%20one%20thing.%20After%20his%20Rafael%20issue%20got%20grounded%2C%20he%20started%20a%20new%20chant.%20Five%20industrialists%2C%20five%20industrialists%2C%20five%20industrialists.%20Gradually%2C%20he%20started%20saying%20Ambani-Adani.%20But%20ever%20since%20the%20elections%20were%20announced%2C%20he%20stopped%20abusing%20Ambani%20and%20Adani.%20Today%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20from%20Telangana%20soil%2C%20he%20must%20declare%20how%20much%20money%20they%20have%20taken%20from%20Ambani%2C%20Adani%3F%20Was%20there%20a%20deal%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20stop%20abusing%20Ambani%20and%20Adani%20overnight%3F%20Zaroor%20daal%20mein%20kucchh%20kaala%20hai%20(something%20is%20wrong).%20You%20abused%20them%20for%20five%20years%20and%20then%20it%20stopped%20overnight%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20counterstrike%20is%20significant%20because%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20of%20favouring%20top%20industrialists.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20has%20also%20said%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20made%2022%20Indians%20%26quot%3Barabpati%20(billionaires)%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Congress%20aims%20to%20make%20crores%20of%20people%20%26quot%3Blakhpati%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20location%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20retort%20is%20also%20significant.%20Telangana%2C%20a%20Congress-ruled%20state%2C%20recently%20signed%20several%20MoUs%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%20totalling%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2012%2C400%20crore%20across%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20flagged%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20repeated%20verbal%20attacks%20on%20wealth%20creators%20and%20top%20industrialists.%20In%20fact%2C%20former%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Gourav%20Vallabh%2C%20who%20recently%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20said%20the%20party%20leadership%20forced%20him%20to%20speak%20against%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20one%20who%20addressed%20a%20press%20conference%20against%20Mr%20Adani.%20But%20after%20a%20SEBI%20probe%20gave%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20I%20told%20the%20senior%20party%20leaders%20to%20drop%20the%20matter.%20But%20they%20didn't%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Telangana%20address%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20a%20habit%20of%20raking%20up%20controversies%20in%20election%20season%20and%20recounted%20how%20he%20had%20taken%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20Rafale%20aircraft%20deal%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715154600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5c0dr3k_modi-rahul_625x300_08_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-2024-lok-sabha-election-why-overnight-silence-pms-ambani-adani-counterstrike-on-rahul-gandhi-5615877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20questioned%20today%20why%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20gone%20silent%20on%20his%20%26quot%3BAmbani-Adani%26quot%3B%20offensive%20since%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2