0pa%20being%20Yuvi%20pa%20just%20made%20eye%20contact%20with%20me%20and%20gestured%20me%20to%20move.%20RP%20Singh%20was%20sitting%20behind%20me%20and%20he%20explained%20that%20it%20was%20Yuvraj's%20seat.%20I%20thought%20I%20missed%20the%20name%20written%20on%20the%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20recalled%20the%20story%20with%20a%20smile.%20%26quot%3BHe%20liked%20to%20scare%20people.%20He%20liked%20scarring%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20leaving%20the%20audience%20in%20splits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20witnessed%20Rohit's%20journey%20since%20the%2037-year-old%20made%20his%20debut%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20as%20a%20teenager%20way%20back%20in%202007.%20Recalling%20his%20first%20impressing%20of%20the%20flamboyant%20opener%2C%20Yuvraj%20joked%3A%20%E2%80%9CVery%20poor%20English.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20funny%20guy.%20From%20the%20streets%20of%20Borivali%20(in%20Mumbai)%2C%20we%20always%20tease%20him.%20But%20a%20great%20guy%20at%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ICC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj's%20final%20season%20as%20an%20active%20cricketer%20came%20under%20Rohit's%20captaincy%20at%20MI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20success%20he's%20had%2C%20he%20has%20never%20changed%20as%20a%20person.%20That's%20the%20beauty%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20Fun-loving%2C%20always%20having%20fun%20with%20the%20guys%2C%20A%20great%20leader%20on%20the%20park%20and%20one%20of%20my%20closest%20friends%20from%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20want%20to%20see%20Rohit%20Sharma%20with%20a%20World%20Cup%20trophy%20and%20a%20World%20Cup%20medal.%20He%20really%20deserves%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20Singh%20who%20wishes%20to%20see%20his%20%26quot%3Bclose%20friend%26quot%3B%20win%20the%20elusive%20T20%20World%20Cup%20next%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBesides%20reaching%20the%20final%20of%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20WTC%20Final%20last%20year%2C%20India%20made%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20under%20Rohit's%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opener%20is%20set%20to%20lead%20the%20'Men%20in%20Blue'%20once%20again%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20USA%2C%20starting%20on%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Rohit's%20presence%20is%20going%20to%20be)%20very%20crucial.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20a%20really%20good%20captain%2C%20a%20sensible%20captain%20who%20takes%20decisions%20well%20under%20pressure.%20And%20he's%20the%20one%20to%20take%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%2C%20who%20is%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20ambassador%2C%20told%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20loss%20to%20Australia%20saw%20India's%20quest%20for%20an%20ICC%20title%20stretch%20to%2010%20years%20with%20their%20last%20victory%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202013%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20feels%20India%20needs%20someone%20with%20Rohit's%20expertise%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20team%20at%20the%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20captain%20when%20we%20lost%20in%20the%20(Cricket%20World%20Cup)%2050-over%20final%20(in%202023).%20He%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20trophies%20as%20a%20captain.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20somebody%20like%20him%20to%20captain%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715148300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvvh7tl9g_rohit-sharma-pc-afp_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvery-poor-english-from-borivali-streets-india-great-on-rohit-sharmas-first-impression-in-team-5609886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20will%20be%20leading%20the%20side%20at%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3